long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Are you ready for turbo racing game fun! Avoid obstacles in the endless tunnel and reach the highest score.

Played with Mouse.

Turbo Racer Game Features
✓ Infinity level
✓ Realistic particle
✓ Basic control
✓ 3D Environment

Finally, you can enjoy these game for free (and more requests will be added)! Turbo Racer Game extension does not contain any hidden ads.
